																																																	<p style="text-indent: 1.25cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;" align="justify"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Función Listar:</span></span></span>
